Install
```````


.. code:: bash

	`[sudo] pip install discord_wt_nickname`




Features
````````

*	online validate nicknames



Usage
`````


.. code:: python

	>>> from discord_wt_nickname import wt_nickname
	
	>>> wt_nickname("@display_name ...")



Examples
````````


.. code:: python

	>>> wt_nickname("@alconafter (Kirill)#1488")
	alconafter
	
	>>> wt_nickname("@invalid_nickname")
	None
